ported\n- Intuitive user interface\n- Shake smoothing\n- Privacy modes\n- Convenient folder navigation\n- Picture adjustments: brightness, contrast, saturation\n- VR Video adjustments: tilt, height, zoom, playback speed\n\nJust download and see it for yourself ! ;)", "short_description": "Exclusive to users that don\u2019t like complications - PLAY\u2019A is the versatile virtual reality video player created to match a busy lifestyle.  Whether it is a simple and intuitive interface, a very hip contemporary design, playback from local file storage or streaming from the network connected servers, PLAY\u2019A does it right and it does it with style! \n\nNavigation is easy in and out of virtual reality. Just jump on a couch and turn it on - you are ready to go!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://playavr.com/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://playavr.com/terms", "publisher_name": "Swearl, LLC", "support_website_url": "https://playavr.com/contact", "website_url": "https://playavr.com/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["MEDIA_PLAYER"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "1003263646927308"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "794560398129231"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "794560398129231"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1617065220, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "794560398129231"}]}, "liveChannel